<div class="category_det_align">
<p>The incumbents work under the close direction of the First Operator or Lead Operator.  They are responsible for maintaining the production output of their assigned production line at the productivity levels designated by department management.  Daily responsibilities include producing quality products at maximum efficiency while meeting high safety standards.  As you will be working in a face paced environment</p><br>

    <p>Ensure that all production equipment is operating safely and at optimum efficiency.  If not, report problem immediately.</p>
